regex.pattern: ^========== Start of cloudvm ram size dump at (?P<timestamp>[^=]+) ==========(?P<body>.*)
^========== Start of system state dump at (?P<timestamp>[^=]+) ==========(?P<body>.*)

^\[pid: (?P<s_pid>\d+)\|app: (?P<s_app>[\-\d]+)\|req: (?P<s_req>[\-\d]+)/(?P<s_worker_reqs>\d+)\] (?P<c_ip>[^ ]+) \((?P<cs_username>[^\)]*)\) \{(?P<cs_vars>\d+) vars in (?P<cs_bytes>\d+) bytes\} \[(?P<timestamp>[^\]]+)\] (?P<cs_method>[A-Z]+) (?P<cs_uri_stem>[^ \?]+)(?:\?(?P<cs_uri_query>[^ ]*))? => generated (?P<sc_bytes>\d+) bytes in (?P<s_runtime>\d+) (?P<rt_unit>\w+) \((?P<cs_version>[^ ]+) (?P<sc_status>\d+)\) (?P<sc_headers>\d+) headers in (?P<sc_header_bytes>\d+) bytes \((?P<s_switches>\d+) switches on core (?P<s_core>\d+)\)(?P<body>.*)
